org.bluedb.api.index

Interface UUIDIndexKeyExtractor<V extends java.io.Serializable>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type of the collection being indexed
    All Superinterfaces:
    KeyExtractor<UUIDKey,V>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface UUIDIndexKeyExtractor<V extends java.io.Serializable>
extends KeyExtractor<UUIDKey,V>
    This is used by the BlueIndex class to extract uuids from each value in the BlueCollection. The value can then be quickly found using those uuids. Note that key extractors are serialized by BlueIndex and for this reason it is NOT recommended to use lambdas or anonymous inner classes to define key extractors.
